    Skyhill Clinic Sdn Bhd Vacancies Staff Nurse

    November 7, 2020

    TOC

    • Job Description
    • Company Overview
    • How To Apply

    Skyhill Clinic Sdn Bhd is looking for new potential candidates to fill in for Staff Nurse position. If you currently looking for new healthcare job opportunities and qualified with the job desc, feel free to apply this job.

    Job Description

    • Candidate must possess at least Diploma/Advanced/Higher/Graduate Diploma in Nursing or equivalent.
    • Required language(s): English, Bahasa Malaysia
    • At least 1 Year(s) of working experience in the related field is required for this position.
    • Preferably Non-Executive specialized in Healthcare - Nurse/Medical Support & Assistant or equivalent.

    Company Overview

    Women Wellness Clinic

    Happy Living with New Normal lifestyle after Covid 19 Health Crisis!
    I am truly blessed we survived during this health Crisis. I really hope we have learned many new things as we are moving forward in good spirit. Every crisis, gives us an opportunity to look ahead and start afresh with a better vision and potentially more substantial methods in achieving our aspiration.
    As we are back on our orderly routine with renewed energy, we continue to make our resolution in providing exceptional insights on the health industry, new normal lifestyles and higher perception towards empowering  nation improving each of everyone quality of life. I believe, we can achieve doing this together as we are in clarity of our mission and vision.
    May we achieve new successes and climb greater heights, from A New Normal to a Brave New World. InsyaAllah.
